Data checked as good (Telemetry 1 SE reflected dip) JPS 09/01/2018;There is a significant drop in the stage during this period. This appears to be genuine because it occured in all of the instrumentation at the station. However, it does not appear in the trend for Nutscale which is in the headwaters. A possible cause of this is the operation of the upstream sluice for the leat for Horner Mill. This would deprive the main channel flow for a period of time.
